title: US warns of Russian capabilities as Ukraine cautions against Western panic
content:
1. US warns of Russian capabilities as Ukraine cautions against Western panic  The Washington Post
  2. Defense Secretary says "conflict is not inevitable" in Ukraine  CBS News
  3. Russia has just two options in front of it, says the top U.S. official in Ukraine  NPR
  4. Pentagon denies Ukraine crisis at '11th hour' but warns attack may be 'imminent'  New York Post
  5. LIVE: U.S. Defense Secretary Austin and General Milley discuss Ukraine  Reuters
